Package se.dat255.bulletinferno.model.map

Interface Summary
EnemyPlacement A link entry between an EnemyDefinitionImpl and a position for which it should be placed in a Slice
MapEnvironment Environment for keeping track of anything map-related.
Obstacle Collidable terrain in the world.
ObstacleDefinition A definition of an Obstacle type.
ObstaclePlacement The type links an ObstacleDefinition to a placement within a Slice.
Segment A Segment is a holder of map slices, building up a part that looks alike in the game.
SegmentDefinition A definition of a Segment type.
SegmentManager Manages the lifetime of Segments in the context of some viewport.
Slice An interface to define the properties of a slice (i.e. a part) in a Segment.
SliceDefinition A definition of a Slice type.
